law.history: Repealed 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 168, sec. 157, effective June 1, 2005; and amended 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 85, sec. 503, effective June 20, 2005. -- Amended 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 325, sec. 25, effective July 13, 1990. -- Created 1984 Ky. Acts ch. 209, sec. 2, effective July 13, 1984.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Tax credit for expenditures for qualifying energy property installed by taxpayer.
metadata.lrc-note: (6/01/2005). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 168 prevails over its amendment in 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 85.
